OL,3,CStorm Dave will ease through Easter
OL,4,CSunday, forecasters say
OL,6,FThe worst of Storm Dave will pass over
OL,7,Fthe United Kingdom during the course
OL,8,Fof Easter Sunday, weather forecasters
OL,9,Fhave said.
OL,11,FAn amber weather alert remains in
OL,12,Fplace for parts of northern England,
OL,13,FScotland and Wales until 3am on Sunday
OL,14,F` with the yellow weather alert
OL,15,Flifting at noon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
