OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775369052
OL,3,CStorm Dave will ease through Easter
OL,4,CSunday, forecasters say
OL,6,FThe Met Office's forecast for Easter
OL,7,FSunday said: "Storm Dave will clear
OL,8,Faway to the northeast... leaving
OL,9,Fsunshine and showers across the UK for
OL,10,FEaster Sunday. The showers look
OL,11,Fparticularly heavy and blustery in the
OL,12,Fnorth."
OL,14,FBut before the severe weather warning
OL,15,Fis lifted, the Met Office said that
OL,16,F"severe gales" are expected across
OL,17,Fcentral and northern areas of the
OL,18,Fcountry in the early hours of Sunday.
