OL,3,CStorm Dave will ease through Easter
OL,4,CSunday, forecasters say
OL,6,FOn Saturday, gusts of wind of up to
OL,7,F66mph were recorded in Capel Curig,
OL,8,Fnorth Wales. Meanwhile, the A66 was
OL,9,Fclosed in both directions due to the
OL,10,Fstrong winds, National Highways said
OL,11,Fin a statement.
OL,13,FThe Energy Networks Association (ENA)
OL,14,F` which represents electricity network
OL,15,Foperators ` warned of potential power
OL,16,Fcuts and issued safety advice
OL,17,Ffollowing the weather warnings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
