OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775369052
OL,3,CStorm Dave will ease through Easter
OL,4,CSunday, forecasters say
OL,6,FIt said in a statement on Saturday:
OL,7,F"The storm has the potential to affect
OL,8,Flocal power infrastructure, increasing
OL,9,Fthe risk of a power cut and fallen
OL,10,Fpower lines.
OL,12,F"Network operators are increasing
OL,13,Fstaffing for operational teams, and
OL,14,Fmoving spare equipment to where the
OL,15,Fweather is expected to be most
OL,16,Fdisruptive, so it's ready to use if
OL,17,Fneeded."
